{"tid":2319415,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生藏六角匙脫罪 官：買傢俬都送","createTime":"2020-12-10T05:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T06:26:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"377e9d06155d0870dd23a13f1e4b68f0d291998e","tid":2319415,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/MUOWJMTD7JCSXMPWZ7WOVRWNWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FMUOWJMTD7JCSXMPWZ7WOVRWNWU%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=10190910\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FMUOWJMTD7JCSXMPWZ7WOVRWNWU%2F&h=97465b6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/MUOWJMTD7JCSXMPWZ7WOVRWNWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n男生藏六角匙脫罪 官：買傢俬都送<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JtqfanOoyVdZvndMTO0KpBS97Ik=/1000x606/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F6UNKVWO6BGEXEK6KRJXPLYQ3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJtqfanOoyVdZvndMTO0KpBS97Ik%3D%2F1000x606%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF6UNKVWO6BGEXEK6KRJXPLYQ3A.jpg&h=458ba849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■裁判官葉啟亮<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月連日大三罷行動期間，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無牌藏對講機罰4,000元<br />\n<br />\n被。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官葉啟亮裁決指，當時未有肺炎疫情，但被告戴鴨舌帽及蒙面，顯然想隱藏身份，其背囊內有防毒面具及濾罐等，種種迹象顯示他是示威者。不過，六角匙本身非特別工具，並非能開鎖的百合匙，有時購買傢俬也會附送用作組裝。案例已表明管有工具的「非法用途」只限束縛人身、侵害人身或入侵處所，但單靠六角匙難以爆竊。<br />\n<br />\n葉官指，被告被捕地點既非商舖、梯間、收銀機或夾萬附近，亦距離堵路位置200米，況且示威者只用膠圍欄及水馬堵路，沒迹象顯示被告用六角匙拆開路邊鐵欄，故裁定罪脫。男生早前承認的無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪則判罰款4,000元。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC835/20"},{"pid":"cefd15c07699285ad8495c6fabd53bc63a23bd3a","tid":2319415,"uid":79793,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"依家判有冇罪係抽咩官?"},{"pid":"470e3c12acc377dc602af128a34c24df5a9d69d9","tid":2319415,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cefd15c07699285ad8495c6fabd53bc63a23bd3a","tid":2319415,"uid":79793,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"依家判有冇罪係抽咩官?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"正常少少既官遲下都無得做啦"},{"pid":"25878698bc565e8f4fd01605bb51e948c8bc5722","tid":2319415,"uid":66447,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cefd15c07699285ad8495c6fabd53bc63a23bd3a","tid":2319415,"uid":79793,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"依家判有冇罪係抽咩官?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"係睇doj記唔記得上訴 <br />\n通常記得就坐硬"},{"pid":"76a0421279848c44511a1221eb94c459ba332c94","tid":2319415,"uid":34722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"案例已表明管有工具的「非法用途」只限束縛人身、侵害人身或入侵處所。居然有官跟案例而唔係「我認為」或者「可以推斷」"},{"pid":"1c0d194029b8b0a2a6df599b2b8b683703ae12bd","tid":2319415,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"咁正常都有得做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e4311a23a01fdc580e3c6ee82909072ea495e2","tid":2319415,"uid":240409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5c5389a1fa1b3e17daee6f8b85de890d00c440d","tid":2319415,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0d194029b8b0a2a6df599b2b8b683703ae12bd","tid":2319415,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"咁正常都有得做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"一半正常一半癲,賭運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69af431e4d97ef101b6974e341c75b3bdbb2b42f","tid":2319415